<h4>Download by Ticker</h4>
<p>The US ETF Constituents dataset is part of the US Equity universe cost. The data file format is one file per ETF per day and each file costs 50 QCC = $0.50 USD. For the full US Equity cost breakdown, see <a href="/docs/v2/lean-cli/datasets/quantconnect/us-equity#06-Price">US Equity</a>. The dataset also requires the <a href="https://www.quantconnect.com/datasets/quantconnect-us-equity-security-master/pricing">US Equity Security Master</a>.</p>

<h4>Download in Bulk</h4>
<p>When you download in bulk, you are billed per file at the same rate: one file per ETF per day at 50 QCC = $0.50 USD.</p>
